%% Diagram: Decision tree for picking an invalidation strategy by content type
%% Type: flowchart
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
flowchart TD
    Start([Need to invalidate])
    Start --> Q1{URL derived<br/>from content?}
    Q1 -->|Yes| Versioned[Versioned URL<br/>1y immutable]
    Q1 -->|No| Q2{Many entries<br/>per source?}

    Q2 -->|No| Q3{Tolerate<br/>brief stale?}
    Q3 -->|Yes| SWR[max-age + SWR]
    Q3 -->|No| PathPurge[Path purge<br/>+ verify]

    Q2 -->|Yes| Q4{Surrogate<br/>keys supported?}
    Q4 -->|Yes| TagPurge[Tag-based purge]
    Q4 -->|No| TagWorkaround[App tag→URL index<br/>then path purge]
